 ::And this scroll being tacked up, the top covered with the Kanji symbols for 'Sprit', 'Hate', and 'Rage' noted at the top and bottom.<br>
The ledgable words read as such.::<br>
'<br>
Those that dare enter my forest, the Netkulos forest and slay my guards, hear me.<br>
I will fight you. If I win, I expect you to pick up and depart. <br>
If I lose, then you will go on your merry way.<br>
If you fit the above categories, you may stop reading here.<br>
For the rest of my message pertains to the Cowardly scum that Dare enter my forest, taking advtange of the guards position and slaying them.<br>
But fear a true battle from a real fighter.<br>
If you are seasons below me, I will give you the benefit of the doubt.<br>
But, if you are within the same circle or higher then myself.<br>
They let it be known, I know your names.<br>
I know where you live.<br>
And I will hunt you down to the ends of Norrath to settle the score.<br>
The names I have encountered so far are as follows:<br>
<br>
Amur. Highelven Wizard. Unguilded.<br>
Menemas. Woodelven somethingorother. &lt;Starspun&gt;<br>
<br>
More names will continue to be listed here of those that dare slay my brothers of the forest, and expect me to turn them aside with a uncaring eye.<br>
<br>
I say, nay. You will be judged on the fields of battle.<br>
That is all.<br>
~Shintou Shinai.<br>
~Protector of the Dark Forest of Nektulos.<br>
'<br>
::And the note ends.:: <p><IMG SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif">Shintou Shinai</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=67.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=67.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=67.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.threadControl?topicID=67.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=67.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=67.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="firionaviefrm1">Firiona Vie General Chat<option value="firionaviefrm2">The Market Square<option value="firionaviefrm4">The Soapbox<option value="firionaviefrm6">Signature Testing<option value="firionaviefrm7">Patch Messages<option value="firionaviefrm8">RP Server Rules<option value="firionaviefrm9">OT/OOC Forum<option value="firionaviefrm10">A Bard for a Day<option value="firionaviefrm11">Announcements<opt